Package fitnessclub

Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
fitnessclub.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
Class meant to represent a fitness class and its information. Contains information about the instructor, start time, class type, studio location and members and guests attending.
Author:
Ashley Berlinski
